{"id": "1504407066712871002", "channel_id": "1504407066712871002", "author_id": "1487626955791663208", "author_name": "lightproud", "content": "## 前瞻：V2.5.1 胚胎融合变化\n\n我们计划在 V2.5.1带来几项胚胎融合调整，敬请注意：\n\n- 胚胎融合会以数值显示而非百分比，普通血肉界域在胚胎融合达到 100 时生成 1 个「胚胎」到手中。\n- 阿格里帕指令卡「不耐的施舍」：胚胎融合翻倍效果现在最多使基础胚胎融合 +100，不受到胚胎融合效果提高加成。\n- 泰旖丝超限爆发「永续圣骸的传承」：如果没有「胚胎」时，不再获得「胚胎」，而是胚胎融合+100，不受到胚胎融合效果提高加成。\n\n这些调整不会影响 V2.5.1 更新之前就拥有的实际能力，但是能够为后续游戏内容更新带来更多的设计空间与信息辨识度。\n\nWe plan to roll out several Embryo Fusion adjustments in V2.5.1. Please take note:\n\n- Embryo Fusion will be displayed as a numerical value rather than a percentage. In the standard Caro Realm, when Embryo Fusion reaches 100, 1 \"Embryo\" will be generated to your hand.\n- Agrippa's Command Card \"Reluctant Alms\": The Embryo Fusion doubling effect will now grant at most +100 base Embryo Fusion, and will not benefit from Embryo Fusion effect bonuses.\n- Thais's Over-Exaltation \"Sacred Relic's Perpetuity\": When there is no \"Embryo\", instead of gaining an \"Embryo\", you will gain +100 Embryo Fusion, which is not affected by Embryo Fusion effect bonuses.\n\nThese adjustments will not affect actual capabilities you already possess prior to the V2.5.1 update, but will provide greater design space and clearer information legibility for subsequent content updates.", "timestamp": "2026-05-14T08:56:35.236000+00:00", "thread_id": "1504407066712871002", "edited_timestamp": "2026-05-14T09:23:13.244000+00:00", "reactions": [{"emoji": "❓", "emoji_id": null, "count": 39}, {"emoji": "agree", "emoji_id": "1400771815076528258", "count": 5}, {"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}, {"emoji": "🇫🇷", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}, {"emoji": "🚮", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}]}
